**Instalar loader de css minimizer**
npm install css-minimizer-webpack-plugin --save-dev


**Instalar loader de Webpack**
npm install css-loader sass-loader sass webpack --save-dev

**Instalar eslint y sus plugin**.

npm install eslint babel-eslint eslint-config-airbnb eslint-plugin-import eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y eslint-plugin-react @babel/eslint-parser

**Instalar pretier**.

npm install prettier eslint-plugin-prettier eslint-config-prettier